{
  "stem": "15393.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Tonight please don't worry about me, I won't come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She went off to work, we were in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Everything was more or less normal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And suddenly toward the evening, rumors begin to spread, the rumors that the night they're closing down the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "All the gates, main and others, are going to be closed up completely and only those who come into the ghetto and go out of the ghetto who have a specific, specific insignia.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In other words, working, it's like a patch or badge or whatever-- more patch than a badge-- with the letter W, which was Wehrmacht, or R, which was Rostov [POLISH], which meant industry-- heavy industry.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Only those working for these institutions will be allowed in and out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Everybody else is taken away and goes to [POLISH] and that's the extermination camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "In other words, no other labor is necessary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "My mother worked for a civilian institution, German institution.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They didn't require any more Jewish labor there, obviously, from that moment on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was a terrible news and it started-- it was spreading very fast.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I realized that there must be a lot to it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ghetto is closed, and we saw, we heard all these goings-on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived immediately behind the embankment, you would call it, the railway embankment, and there were gates here and there alongside this embankment.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I thought, God Almighty, what is going to happen?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother doesn't have any of these-- neither of these two, rather.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She will obviously want to come back to the ghetto in the morning, and it's not easy to come back into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have to join a group coming back from work night shift.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
